txt.en: Sûhalar hooks can be found along the Rammas.\n\nYou should remove hooks from the top of the Rammas.
'The Sûhalar have used crude hooks to quickly climb the Out-wall. If you see any of these hooks, make sure to destroy them.'
Sûhalar hooks can be found along the Rammas.\n\nYou should remove hooks from the top of the Rammas.
Easterlings have invaded the northern Rammas and it is up to you to see them off the Out-wall.
